We’re working on adding AprilTag-based autonomous to our 2025 robot using two PhotonVision ThriftyCams and an Orange Pi 5. We’re using PhotonLib version 2025.3.1 and a full-field AprilTag layout.

We’ve written a VisionSubsystemFullField class with two PhotonPoseEstimator instances (one per camera), using the constructor:

